Listen to an ANC Mpumalanga supporter accuse Deputy President David ‘DD’ Mabuza of being a murderer and a womaniser. The man, who supports David Dube to take over as ANC provincial chairperson at the provincial general council (PGC) in September, did not take kindly to Mabuza’s endorsement of the current acting provincial chairperson, Mandla Ndlovu. In this video, Dube can be seen laughing and enjoying himself while his supporter is hurling a volley of insults at the deputy president. WATCH BELOW: